title: 2002 WAFF Championship squads
text:
The <a href="2002%20WAFF%20Championship">2002 WAFF Championship</a> is an international <a href="Association%20football">football</a> tournament held in Syria from 30 August to 7 September 2002. The six national teams involved in the tournament were required to register a squad of 23 players, including three goalkeepers. Only players in these squads were eligible to take part in the tournament.
